# Lower-stratum negated view (analysis sec 4.5 R9): blk strictly below mid
# (mid derived via raw->step->mid). Pins A-vs-B observational equivalence
# across a differential blk flip.
#
# Batch 1: feed three keys; block key 2. out = {(1,10),(3,30)}
#          (mid={(1,10),(2,20),(3,30)}, blk={2}).
# Batch 2: block key 1 too. out = {(3,30)}.
# Batch 3: unblock key 2. out = {(2,20),(3,30)}.
# Batch 4: same-batch flap +block 3 / -block 3 (nets zero). out unchanged.
batch
+ feed 1 10
+ feed 2 20
+ feed 3 30
+ block 2
end

batch
+ block 1
end

batch
- block 2
end

batch
+ block 3
- block 3
end
